track_title: Long way drive to the parking

track_notes: This is a nice summit, it can be done in winter with snowshoes. Park is ok up to Roure, plenty room on summit (no trees, no cross), nice panorama on the Alps

This is a nice walk to this summit, there is a car park, many room, at the village Roure, you must go to the Arboretum using a small road for 2km. The walk is easy, no danger event if you come in winter time with snow-shoes. On summit there is no cross, no trees, but plenty room for antenna. The panorama is wonderfull.
track_title: Easy and nice in summer and in winter
